Shadow Wing::

She kept flying.  She climbed in altitude.  She flet the cold wind blow 
against her face. She could see the light of the sun just creeping over the 
horizon.  She flew north and hoped she would be left alone there.  Al she 
wanted was to survive alone.  She knew she could.  She flew higher yet into 
the air.  She now was way above the mountains and soaring high on the cold 
winds.
